description:
Fengxian is the former Princess of Verdigris House, a high ranking courtesan known for her cold demenour and unparalleled skills in go and shougi. 
She arranged the situation there she got pregnant with Lakans child (MaoMao) in hope he will redeem her contract. Unfortunate circumstances related to Lakans father and famine in the Empire crushed these plans as he had to stay for 3 years on the Empires border. Falling from grace she had to become a regular "street walker" and contacted syphilis, which she refused to treat. Which led to her going mentally ill.
name: Fengxian
